languages.text: Спустя пару десятилетий он пал жертвой покушения, организованного криминальным картелем. Говорят, к устранению Инквизитора была причастна Миссия Касбаллики, уставшая от непримиримого служителя закона.
A few decades later, he was assassinated by a criminal cartel. Some say the Kasballica Mission, sick of the unrelenting servant of the law, was involved in the Inquisitor's killing.

languages.text: 数十年后，他遭到了某个犯罪集团的暗杀。有人说，卡斯巴利卡犯罪集团与他的死有关，因为他们受够了这位冥顽不化的律法忠仆。
languages.original_text: A few decades later, he was assassinated by a criminal cartel. Some say the Kasballica Mission, sick of the unrelenting servant of the law, was involved in the Inquisitor's killing.

traits.locale_text: 数十年后，他遭到了某个犯罪集团的暗杀。有人说，卡斯巴利卡犯罪集团与他的死有关，因为他们受够了这位冥顽不化的律法忠仆。

languages.text: Einige Jahrzehnte später wurde er von einem Verbrecherkartell ermordet. Manche sagen, die Kasballica-Mission sei des gnadenlosen Dieners des Gesetzes überdrüssig geworden und habe etwas mit dem Tod des Inquisitors zu tun.
languages.original_text: A few decades later, he was assassinated by a criminal cartel. Some say the Kasballica Mission, sick of the unrelenting servant of the law, was involved in the Inquisitor's killing.

traits.locale_text: Jahrzehnte später wurde er von einem Verbrecherkartell ermordet. Manche sagen, die Kasballica-Mission sei des gnadenlosen Dieners des Gesetzes überdrüssig geworden und habe etwas mit seinem Tod zu tun.

languages.text: Il fut assassiné quelques décennies plus tard par un cartel criminel. Certains affirment que la Mission de la Kasballica, lasse de cet infatigable serviteur de la loi, serait impliquée dans sa mort.
languages.original_text: A few decades later, he was assassinated by a criminal cartel. Some say the Kasballica Mission, sick of the unrelenting servant of the law, was involved in the Inquisitor's killing.

traits.locale_text: Il fut assassiné des décennies plus tard par un cartel criminel. Certains affirment que la Mission de la Kasballica, lasse de cet infatigable serviteur de la loi, serait impliquée dans sa mort.

languages.text: Unas décadas después, fue asesinado a manos de un cártel criminal. Algunos dicen que la misión Kasballica, que estaba harta del implacable sirviente de la ley, tomó parte en su muerte.
languages.original_text: A few decades later, he was assassinated by a criminal cartel. Some say the Kasballica Mission, sick of the unrelenting servant of the law, was involved in the Inquisitor's killing.

traits.locale_text: Décadas después, fue asesinado a manos de un cártel criminal. Algunos dicen que la misión Kasballica, que estaba harta del implacable sirviente de la ley, está relacionada con su muerte.

languages.text: 数十年後、男は犯罪集団に暗殺された。審問官のたゆまぬ遵法思想にたまりかねたカスバリカ聖務団が異端審問官の殺害に関与したという言う者もいる。
languages.original_text: A few decades later, he was assassinated by a criminal cartel. Some say the Kasballica Mission, sick of the unrelenting servant of the law, was involved in the Inquisitor's killing.

traits.locale_text: 数十年後、男は犯罪集団に暗殺された。この死にはカスバリカ聖務団が絡んでいて、審問官のたゆまぬ遵法思想にたまりかねたのだと言う者もいる。

languages.text: Birkaç on yıl sonra bir suç karteli tarafından suikasta uğradı. Bazıları, Engizisyoncu'nun öldürülmesinden, kanunların yılmaz hizmetkârından bıkan Kasballica Misyonu'nun sorumlu olduğunu söyler.
